Botas,

You need to put your Dao package in the component scam tag at dispatcher-servlet.xml.

    &lt;context:component-scan base-package=&quot;controllers,dao&quot; /&gt;

Change your applicationContext.xml to this

    &lt;property name=&quot;packagesToScan&quot;&gt;
    	&lt;list&gt;
    		&lt;value&gt;dao.**.*&lt;/value&gt;
    	&lt;/list&gt;
    &lt;/property&gt;

Now every class, even in sub-packages, will be found by spring.

Apart from package sanning, you seem to have incorrectly defined your sessionFactory.

As you are using spring 4 and hibernate 4 you should define it as:

    &lt;bean id=&quot;sessionFactory&quot;
        class=&quot;org.springframework.orm.hibernate4.LocalSessionFactoryBean&quot;&gt;

Also try defining the transaction manager as:

   

    &lt;bean id=&quot;transactionManager&quot;
        class=&quot;org.springframework.orm.hibernate4.HibernateTransactionManager&quot;&gt;
          &lt;property name=&quot;sessionFactory&quot; ref=&quot;sessionFactory&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/bean&gt;

