At the line where you calculate the median

    double medianIndex = (startIndex + endIndex - 1) / 2;

you are doing integer division as both sides are integers, since `startIndex` and `endIndex` are ints. Either cast one of them or both to double or make the divisor `2` a double. The easiest way to fix could be:

